  abstract	= {It is known that a keV scale sterile neutrino is a good
		  warm dark matter candidate. We study how this possibility
		  could be realized in the context of gauge extensions of the
		  standard model. The na\'ive expectation leads to large
		  thermal overproduction of sterile neutrinos in this setup.
