		  out-of-equilibrium decay of the other right-handed
		  neutrinos of the model to dilute the present density of the
		  keV sterile neutrinos and achieve the observed dark matter
		  density. We present the universal requirements that should
		  be satisfied by the gauge extensions of the standard model,
		  containing right-handed neutrinos, to be viable models of
